    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a gem. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today! It looks great and drives even better. I've taken good care of it, so it's got plenty of life left for its next owner. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
