      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2011 Porsche Cayman S represents a pinnacle of mid-engine balance, powered by a 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six featuring Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) for optimized combustion and throttle response. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle, ensuring a mechanical connection lost in modern iterations. The chassis utilizes a MacPherson strut suspension geometry that provides exceptional lateral stiffness and telepathic steering feedback. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston aluminum monoblock fixed calipers over vented and cross-drilled rotors, offering superb thermal resistance. This example is mechanically robust with a documented service history, though it shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car. It remains a visceral, analog machine ready for technical apexes.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Minor wear only. Fully operational.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a fantastic example of a well-cared-for daily driver that strikes a balance between luxury and utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss luster, though a careful walk-around will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from parallel parking. The alloy wheels are in great shape with only very light curb rash on the front right. Inside, the cabin remains a pleasant place to be; the upholstery is clean and free of any smoke or pet odors, showing only slight softening of the leather on the driver's seat bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display operates as intended, including the dual-zone climate control and the sunroof. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with the most recent multi-point inspection confirming that the brakes and suspension are in solid working order. The engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts crisply. It is a reliable, attractive car that is ready for many more miles of dependable service.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both reliability and sophisticated design. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and optimal road performance. Featuring a well-preserved exterior and a refined cabin environment, this automobile offers an exceptional balance of prestige and value. We invite discerning buyers to experience the dependable quality and smooth handling that define this distinguished selection.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
